# CommonMark Leaf Block Converter in C

> Implement a Markdown-to-HTML converter in C handling CommonMark leaf blocks (headings, code blocks, HTML blocks, thematic breaks, paragraphs, tabs). The converter reads from stdin and writes HTML to stdout, must compile via make, and must not use any external Markdown library.

---

## Task Configuration

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Difficulty | hard |
| Category | programming |
| Agent Timeout | 7200s |
| Verifier Timeout | 600s |
| Internet Access | Disabled |
| CPUs / Memory | 2 / 4096 MB |

